yTime":"2020-07-10T14:53:21.000Z","msg":"唔做初選本土咪一撚樣𠝹到冇撚左議席<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔係應該更加說服更多人投本土咩？反而叫人唔好參加初選<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n依家就係要有個大眾認受嘅配票抵抗對家配票嘅力量呀嘛<br />\n<br />\n人地出黎選都未驚你驚人偷到你資料<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁多野驚船頭驚鬼船尾驚賊，勇武出黎打唔撚驚嘅！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1b5ad29a13aeba837393f66a122e1ff006ff88b","tid":2102583,"uid":30506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7440b8aa23897f15984e41b138b2c297547cf650","tid":2102583,"uid":30506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T14:33:39.000Z","msg":"點解忽然有種秋意<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T16:43:38.000Z","msg":"係2014年嘅秋意"},{"pid":"d757372616ceaacc236b7c399eae778657fe50a5","tid":2102583,"uid":30506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bcd0937bb42420827c7ececcb7ba440bb61111dc","tid":2102583,"uid":43062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T14:53:21.000Z","msg":"唔做初選本土咪一撚樣𠝹到冇撚左議席<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔係應該更加說服更多人投本土咩？反而叫人唔好參加初選<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n依家就係要有個大眾認受嘅配票抵抗對家配票嘅力量呀嘛<br />\n<br />\n人地出黎選都未驚你驚人偷到你資料<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁多野驚船頭驚鬼船尾驚賊，勇武出黎打唔撚驚嘅！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T16:44:45.000Z","msg":"最多聲氣就係呢班所謂本土<br />\n人哋做嘢唔support 都算<br />\n淨係識搵問題<br />\n啲問題仲要係雞蛋裏挑骨頭嗰隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d435f76730755f715624c1ff8fc7ce81e13ffca","tid":2102583,"uid":30506,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T16:50:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我不是呼籲不要投本土派，但是現在自稱「本土派」去參與初選的人，是否你心中所想的本土派？或只是披着本土皮囊的泛民？</blockquote><br />\n連參選本土派嘅都屈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係咪得熱狗可以係本土派<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb886114b22e22e202b7d3ab62cce3bcf5f63540","tid":2102583,"uid":30506,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T16:52:05.000Z","msg":"呢班人最叻就係叫人行條奇怪路<br />\n唔信泛民都信鍾庭耀吖<br />\n<br />\n叫人就算聽日投都唔投本土<br />\n差在未叫九月投白票<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb6a154c8b605322a4fda9592f929fe3dd07f224","tid":2102583,"uid":30506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5444c35b08b49d68b9c50b88c5357bd9f52ec6b3","tid":2102583,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2ba29bdf3dcfb148236a8a434d5a0392ed88dd7d","tid":2102583,"uid":30506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e21ef0c34b64ac3a71493d88b6f600cdf5decd23","tid":2102583,"uid":21545,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T14:32:54.000Z","msg":"那麼知道了初選有多糟糕後，可以怎樣做？其實也有不參與初選的候選人可供選擇<br />\n<br />\n咁都唔係熱狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T14:37:09.000Z","msg":"問佢哋可以點 就話照返往年投票咁得㗎喇<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁我搞初選嚟做咩 畀你講到一無是處<br />\n借吓iPad 又話本來可以用喺手足度<br />\n咁叻你嚟搞"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T14:37:58.000Z","msg":"部I pad可以點幫手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T16:55:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bjXZ9eM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbjXZ9eM.png&h=e1d0584d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n鬧到冇嘢好鬧"},{"pid":"c1294255ca7864e3fc19af6716e8af8fc51cc327","tid":2102583,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T16:55:52.000Z","msg":"那麼知道了初選有多糟糕後，可以怎樣做？其實也有不參與初選的候選人可供選擇，你亦可以思考「三不投」的正當性、深入查閱每個候選人的論述、政黨、政綱、政績，又或是理解香港以往的政治局面，研究不同派系的利弊，跟身邊人分享你對初選的看法，<strong><span class=\"red\">這大概會比漫無目的地參與更具價值</span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n即係學口交部齋噏就得，按兵不動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43733ccdc35614c7b0328ec9f21b90db3f312357","tid":2102583,"uid":66260,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T17:20:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bb0d4e3cf14c81abab2a5442f85539f151577fd3","tid":2102583,"uid":43062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"43733ccdc35614c7b0328ec9f21b90db3f312357","tid":2102583,"uid":66260,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T17:20:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T18:38:37.000Z","msg":"呢班人個諗法完全睇唔透<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我有好盡力去理解佢地嘅憂慮同擔心<br />\n<br />\n除左不停拉埋醫護罷工名單外洩黎講資料會被賣，一味就係話呢個圍爐初選，泛民食哂啲票個個含淚要大選含陣投<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 總之死都話係假本土邊個邊個好鬼<br />\n<br />\n屌你出黎參選個個都未驚，都唔明投個個驚乜柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n驚得過勇武上場打街戰？"},{"pid":"beb6d2deafde1c3648ce45c41253022f2a78c708","tid":2102583,"uid":43062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"43733ccdc35614c7b0328ec9f21b90db3f312357","tid":2102583,"uid":66260,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T17:20:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T18:44:04.000Z","msg":"35+ 係國安法下幾乎冇咩可能，議會有幾有用你我都知，咁係咪等於唔洗表態<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 坐係度就最有用<br />\n<br />\n死都話泛民一定𠝹本土然後大家要跪住含<br />\n唔初選等同保皇含啦屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n問佢地唔做議會線唔做初選可以點，又串你「錦鋰有咩高見」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 溝通唔到啊大佬"},{"pid":"da4f0c8e664c038f2168130730c8c07f83a1180e","tid":2102583,"uid":1251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T18:57:20.000Z","msg":"同輔仁黨差唔多<br />\n係咁話人屈佢係熱狗<br />\n但立場同熱狗一撚樣"},{"pid":"6069ccae44d609621f6bfc94e62ccd4bab6cd96e","tid":2102583,"uid":82829,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T19:01:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}